    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Taxes or imposts paid to a prince or state, by another prince or state or by vassals, in homage, acknowledgement of submission, or as the price of peace, security, and protection.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
